item.description:
Join us for Dinner at Fresh Catch in Mansfield for some excellent seafood.  There are many locations for the Fresh Catch and we have chosen the Mansfield Location to have a fun  Meetup dinner.  The dinner prices are very reasonable.  There is something on the menu for everyone.  You will find Sushi, Seafood, Chicken & Meat on the menu.  There are excellent reviews on Yelp.com.  The Fresh Catch is located in a strip mall in Mansfield. 

So come and join us for excellent New England Seafood. 

 

 

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Thursday, July 7th @  6:30pm

Fresh Catch

30 Chauncy Street

Mansfield, MA 02048

(508) 339-5187

http://www.freshcatchinc.com/

 

 

Meeting Place: Please meet outside the front door or inside the restaurants ask for Alison or Jeanne

Please Note:

If you are running very late or not attending please call the restaurant so they can let us know.  Here is my cell # 617-435-2359  Jeanne

Organizers: Alison and Jeanne

Event Fee: [Current] Annual Members - FREE, Members - $2 each; $6 to become a 2011 Annual Member

Min/Max: No minimum. Alison and Jeanne will dine by themselves if need be.[:)] Due to the size of the restaurant, the max is set at 10 people.

Guests: Annual members may bring 1 free guest to this event. 

RSVP Deadline: 8pm on Wednesday July 6th. Any changes made after this time may not be seen by an Event Organizer prior to the event.

Please bring cash. You are responsible for your portion of the bill including drinks, food, shared food, tax, and tip.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Directions:

Route 95 to exit 7A toward Mansfield and go about 1.4 miles and turn left onto Route 106 / Chauncey St. Go 0.9 miles to #30 on your right. It is located in a small strip mall.
